				\begin{document}$$\:{StO}_{2}=\frac{{C}_{HbO2}^{S}}{{C}_{HbO2}^{S}+\:{C}_{Hb}^{S}}\:\cdot\:\:100\:$$\end{document}

The performance of the nonlinear regression model was assessed using the coefficient of determination R2 which indicates how well-calculated absorbance values for each pixel in the image are estimated by the model. It is mathematically defined by Eq. 6:6\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
